economic policy in the late 1950s\h\h

10
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:43,840
that caused the deaths of\h
tens of millions of people.”

11
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:49,120
Now the idea that China’s population has\h
fallen for the first time in 50 years\h\h

12
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:54,160
doesn’t sound controversial.\h
But we’re talking about China,\h\h

13
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:59,600
