16
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:12,480
Chinese leader Xi Jinping’s favorite\h
breakfast food? Definitely state secret.

17
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:20,720
According to the Financial Times, China’s\h
population fell below 1.4 billion in 2020.\h\h

18
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:25,440
Those population numbers come from\h
China’s latest 10-year census,\h\h

19
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:29,840
which hasn’t been publicly released\h
yet. The Financial Times got their\h\h

20
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:34,080
scoop from anonymous sources claiming\h
to be “familiar with the research.”

21
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:40,240
They added that “The figure was considered\h
very sensitive and would not be released until\h\h

22
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:45,600
multiple government departments had reached a\h
consensus on the data and its implications.”

23
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:53,120
Well after the Financial Times ran this story,\h
Chinese government departments reached a consensus\h\h

24
00:01:53,120 --> 00:02:01,680
