00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:04,720
What are they going to do, make\h
a communist version of Tinder?

123
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:10,640
But don’t worry, because it’s not just about\h
matchmaking. It’s also about getting married\h\h

124
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:15,680
younger. There have been proposals that the\h
government should lower the marriage age to 18.

125
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:19,760
But what happens if propaganda\h
and social pressure,\h\h

126
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:23,920
not to mention the matchmaking prowess\h
of the Politburo, still isn’t enough?

127
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:28,240
Remember what I said earlier about\h
how the one-child policy created\h\h

128
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:32,240
