00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:38,560
Well some experts “fear that officials will\h
reorient the gigantic family-planning bureaucracy,\h\h

130
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:43,520
which enforced restrictions through forced\h
abortions, sterilizations and steep fines,\h\h

131
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,840
toward pushing women to have children.”

